 <metadata>
  <name>RTR - Eton Hill Road-Bury Road-Spring Lane</name>
  <desc>Loop around Lidl and back down Stand Lane to the market, then make you way down Church St West toward festival gardens.  At Festival Gardens turn right on to Cross Lane and then on to Eton Hill Road. From here turn left on Bury Road and then right on to Spring Lane before turning left and Blackburn Street and return to the market</desc>
  <author>
   <name>Paul Cox</name>
   <link href="https://www.strava.com/athletes/90628842"/>
  </author>
